                                                                            <div class="article-head">
                                            <h1 class="article-headline">College basketball scandal updates: Arizona recruit reportedly hires lawyer</h1>
                                                                                            <h2 class="article-subline article-subline-tight">Get caught up on the FBI's investigation into corruption in college basketball</h2>
                                                                                                                                        


    <ul class="article-author row" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" itemprop="author" section="author"><li class="author-name article-byline-last-author">
                                            by
                                        <span itemprop="name">CBS Sports Staff</span>
                </li>
            
            
                    
        <li class="date-published">
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
            <span class="date-original-reading-time">
